snippet.title: Paw Paw Destiny 🎮 trailer B
snippet.description:
Should not have been born? A secret story(cosmic horror comedy) that your buddy(cat/dog) before meets you.
http://daiyu.studio/pawpawdestiny
🐱Paw Paw Destiny🐶

- Level up your sense of humor and art, while playing!
- Solve social problems whiling travel around the world in a funny way!
- Cat? or Dog? customize your original main character as you like!
- Up to you play mode cozy / dark, according to your mood.

🎮Steam
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2328380
🎮Epic Games Store
https://store.epicgames.com/p/paw-paw-destiny-843848
💻itch.io
https://daiyustudio.itch.io/paw-paw-destiny
📱Google Play
https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.daiyustudio.pawpawdestiny

[Play to Donate]
By your playing, profits from this game will be donated to trusted animal shelters globally.
If you agree, please join us! also, please share.

💫Daiyu.studio (developer)
https://daiyu.studio
